               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, with Psalter of the Virgin, መዝሙረ፡ ድንግል።</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="181r">Fols 1r–181r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2701Dawit">Psalter</title>

                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="148v" facs="003">Fols 1r–148v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3985Mazmura">Mazmura
                                                  Dǝngǝl</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ውዳሴ፡ ዕበይኪ፡ ማርያም፡ እንተ፡ ጸሐፈ፡ በእቅሙ፡
                      እስመ፡ ዖፈ፡ ሕለት፡ ገብርኪ፡ ለወልድኪ፡ ሤጠ፡ ደሙ።
                      መዝሙረ፡ ድንግል፡ ይኩን፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ትርጓሜ፡ ስሙ፡
                      እምቃለ፡ ዳዊት፡ አስተዋጺኦ፡ እምጥንቱ፡ እስከ፡ ተፍጻሙ፡
                      ለዘወደሰኪ፡ ባርኪ፡ እሙ።</incipit>
                    <note>Opening Verse</note>
                    <note>Psalm 118 does not contain the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters</note>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="148v" to="160r" facs="151">Fols 148v–160r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1828Mahale">Book of Odes</title></msItem>
